      • isRoot

        public boolean isRoot(NodeDiff node)
        Description copied from class: VersionCompareHierarchyBuilderImpl
        This method is a shortcut in recursion when hierarchy has to be built among the nodes. Always return with false by default. Clients may override to ensure better performance.

        Returns true if the node argument representing a terminology component is a root node in the associated terminology. Otherwise false.
